{"id":"extended-diagnostics/NG8105","title":"NG8105: Missing `let` keyword in an *ngFor expression\n\n在 `*ngFor` 表示式中缺少 `let` 關鍵字","contents":"<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/extended-diagnostics/NG8105.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng8105-missing-let-keyword-in-an-ngfor-expression在-ngfor-表示式中缺少-let-關鍵字\">NG8105: Missing `let` keyword in an *ngFor expression\n\n在 `*ngFor` 表示式中缺少 `let` 關鍵字<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8105#ng8105-missing-let-keyword-in-an-ngfor-expression在-ngfor-表示式中缺少-let-關鍵字\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  <div class=\"diagnostic-description\">\n    <h2 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"說明\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8105#說明\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <h2 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8105#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">當 <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code> 中使用的表示式缺少 <code>let</code> 關鍵字時，會發出此診斷資訊。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This diagnostic is emitted when an expression used in <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a></code> is missing the <code>let</code> keyword.</p>\n\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  // The `let` keyword is missing in the `*<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a>` expression.\n  template: `&lt;div *<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a>=\"item of items\"&gt;{{ item }}&lt;/div&gt;`,\n  // …\n})\nclass MyComponent {\n  items = [1, 2, 3];\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-resolve-the-problem\" translation-result=\"on\">如何解決此問題<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8105#how-to-resolve-the-problem\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">How to resolve the problem<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8105#how-to-resolve-the-problem\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">新增缺失的 <code>let</code> 關鍵字。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Add the missing <code>let</code> keyword.</p>\n\n<code-example format=\"typescript\" language=\"typescript\">\n\nimport {<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>} from '@angular/core';\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  // The `let` keyword is now present in the `*<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a>` expression,\n  // no diagnostic messages are emitted in this case.\n  template: `&lt;div *<a href=\"api/common/NgFor\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngFor</a>=\"let item of items\"&gt;{{ item }}&lt;/div&gt;`,\n  // …\n})\nclass MyComponent {\n  items = [1, 2, 3];\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/NgFor\n - api/core/Component\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8105#description\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8105#how-to-resolve-the-problem\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8105#ng8105-missing-let-keyword-in-an-ngfor-expression在-ngfor-表示式中缺少-let-關鍵字\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8105#如何解決此問題\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8105#說明\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/extended-diagnostics/NG8105.md?message=docs(...)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}